160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 06:14:20 +08:00\">18h 20m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>只能说 tibo 调教成功了，让我从 plus 升级到了 pro 套餐</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17890339\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6d76/18c3/380444_normal.png?m=1548659685\" alt=\"ixuefeng\" data-uid=\"380444\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>6</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/ixuefeng\">ixuefeng</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 07:32:24 +08:00\">17h 2m ago via iPhone</span> \n                    \n                    <p>现在不能停止执行，补充信息后再按调整后的要求继续执行了？今天发现只能作为后续队列任务，等前一个任务执行完了再执行补充的这个要求。</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17890359\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e915/a64b/151090_normal.png?m=1602590322\" alt=\"Oo0\" data-uid=\"151090\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>7</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/Oo0\">Oo0</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 08:06:46 +08:00\">16h 28m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>卧槽，还没蹬完呢</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17890362\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/dc29/d71f/830608_normal.png?m=1784535541\" alt=\"nxc8335\" data-uid=\"830608\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>8</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/nxc8335\">nxc8335</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 08:09:58 +08:00\">16h 25m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>reset 之神诚不欺我啊哈哈哈哈哈</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17890543\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/943b/33bb/265618_normal.png?m=1758071286\" alt=\"zx9481\" data-uid=\"265618\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>13</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/zx9481\">zx9481</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 09:15:43 +08:00\">15h 19m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>codex 这个重置会改变周限制的重置时间，昨天本来下周一重置的，今天重置完变成下周三了。<br>虽然 cladue 不怎么重置，但是重置不会改变时间<br>只能说 codex 没有想象中的这么大方，相当于用自己的时间换额度</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17890570\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6084f765bdce7ad1ecd95afe1b8bc669?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"Thesara\" data-uid=\"473450\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>14</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/Thesara\">Thesara</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 09:21:11 +08:00\">15h 14m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>@<a href=\"/member/zx9481\">zx9481</a> 感觉 codex 这几次重置应该蛮多人没用太多就重置了，实际上他们应该也没有送出去太多</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17890602\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"htt